<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Provisional NOC Letter - Renewal Multi Owner</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .page-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .page {
            background-color: white;
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 15px;
            page-break-after: always;
        }

        .border-frame {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 2px dotted #333;
            padding: 4px;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .pattern-border {
            flex-grow: 1;
            border: 1px double #333;
            padding: 40px 50px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Standard Frame Borders */
        .page::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px;
            left: 5px;
            right: 5px;
            bottom: 5px;
            border: 2px solid #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .page::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            bottom: 10px;
            border: 4px double #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 80%;
            opacity: 0.1;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .watermark img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .content-area {
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #000;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .header-logo {
            height: 80px;
            width: auto;
        }

        .doc-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 12pt;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .ref-number {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .date-line {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .section-header {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        /* Table Styling */
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        table,
        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid black;
        }

        th {
            padding: 6px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        td {
            padding: 6px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .center-text {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .subject {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .sig-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
        }

        .digital-note {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        @media print {
            body {
                background-color: white;
            }

            .page {
                box-shadow: none;
                margin: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="page-container">

        <!-- PAGE 1 -->
        <div class="page">
            <div class="border-frame">
                <div class="pattern-border">
                    <div class="watermark">
                        <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Watermark">
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-area">
                        <div class="logo-container">
                            <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Webel Logo" class="header-logo">
                        </div>

                        <div class="doc-title">
                            Provisional NOC of IT/ITeS Renting (Application Number: <%= data?._application_number %>)
                        </div>

                        <div class="ref-number">
                            <%= data?._ref_number %>
                        </div>

                        <div class="date-line">
                            Date: <%= data?._current_date %>
                        </div>

                        <div class="section-header">Applicants Details:</div>
                        <table>
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th style="width: 40px;">Sl No.</th>
                                    <th style="width: 25%;">Applicants Name</th>
                                    <th>Address</th>
                                    <th style="width: 110px;">GSTN/PAN Number</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <% if (data?._applicants && data?._applicants.length> 0) { %>
                                    <% data?._applicants.forEach(function(applicant, index) { %>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="center-text">
                                                <%= index + 1 %>
                                            </td>
                                            <td class="bold">
                                                <%= applicant?._name %>
                                            </td>
                                            <td>
                                                <%= applicant?._address %>
                                            </td>
                                            <td class="center-text">
                                                <%= applicant?._tax_id %>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <% }); %>
                                            <% } %>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>

                        <div class="subject">
                            Sub: Permission towards sublet of space of <%= data?._sublet_area_sqft %> sq. ft. super
                                built up area at <%= data?._space_description %>
                        </div>

                        <div class="salutation">Sir,</div>

                        <p>
                            This has reference to your (self declaration letter with UDIN: <span class="bold">
                                <%= data?._udin %>
                            </span>) regarding the permission for subletting the space to M/S <span class="bold">
                                <%= data?._tenant_name %>
                            </span> at <%= data?._space_description %>.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            We would like to confirm our ‘No Objection’ for sub-letting the <%= data?._sublet_area_sqft
                                %> sq. ft. space to M/S <span class="bold">
                                    <%= data?._tenant_name %>
                                </span> for carrying out "<%= data?._activity_type %>" activities as declared by M/S
                                    <span class="bold">
                                        <%= data?._tenant_name %>
                                    </span> vide their letter dated <%= data?._tenant_letter_date %>.
                                        Your Provisional NOC is effective from <%= data?._noc_start_date %> to <%=
                                                data?._noc_end_date %>.
                                                The NOC would lapse automatically as soon as the said tenancies are
                                                expired by influx of time or the same are determined earlier.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- PAGE 2 -->
        <div class="page">
            <div class="border-frame">
                <div class="pattern-border">
                    <div class="watermark">
                        <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Watermark">
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-area">
                        <div class="logo-container">
                            <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Webel Logo" class="header-logo">
                        </div>

                        <p>
                            You are advised to comply all legal formalities regarding agreement with your tenants and
                            inform NDITA about the existence of the said firm in Sector-V area.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            You will have required to pay permission fees @ Rs.<%= data?._permission_fee_rate %>/- per
                                sq. ft. (permission fees is subject to change from time to time) of the super built up
                                area along with applicable goods & services taxes to W.B.E.I.D.C. Ltd by the 7th day of
                                every calendar month. Such fees shall be paid in advance in every month, irrespective of
                                your receiving rent from the tenant and the non-payment of Permission fees or any kind
                                of non-compliance may cause automatic cancellation/withdrawal of the NOC granted.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            Moreover, you are requested to inform us about the vacancy and fill up of premises within
                            the month of its happening otherwise permission fees will be charged upto date as mentioned
                            in the agreement without any reversal thereon.
                        </p>

                        <p>Thanking you,</p>

                        <div class="signature-block">
                            <span class="sig-title">Authorised Signatory</span>
                            <span class="sig-title">For Managing Director, Webel</span>
                            <div class="digital-note">(This document is digitally signed and does not require physical
                                signature)</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>